snippet: Tottenham Hotspur kept up the pressure on the Premier League's top four after coming from behind to beat 10-man Southampton 4-1 thanks to two goals from Dele Alli and one apiece by Harry Kane and Son Heung-min on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur kept up the pressure on the Premier League's top four after coming from behind to beat 10-man Southampton 4-1 thanks to two goals from Dele Alli and one apiece by Harry Kane and Son Heung-min on Wednesday.

headline.main: Alli Double Helps Spurs Sink 10-Man Southampton
headline.print_headline: Alli Double Helps Spurs Sink 10-Man Southampton
